Package io.rxson.reactive

Interface Emitter<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the value type
public interface Emitter<T>
Author:
Mohamed Aly Bou Hanane

Wrapper API around a json stream Subscriber for emitting received stream chunks followed by zero or one onError/onComplete.
